[font=comic sans ms][size=7pt]Don't post anything at all, just private message me or don't. This is my Development thread which will be updated daily.[/size][/font] [img]http://i145.photobucket.com/albums/r220/majesstik1/Threads/funny.gif[/img] [TOP]
[center][img]http://img825.imageshack.us/img825/772/69498630293d607m3.jpg[/img][/center] [center][size=14pt]Best Advanced 735 Loading 742![/size][/center]
[center][size=18pt]Info:[/size][/center]
This is the best advanced 735 loading 742, that was professionally recoded and added cache client by my 2 cousins that both are extreme coders. I helped via Source part they told me what to add and what to leave out or delete. My cousins did the maps, cache, and recoding all the 317 to a 742. I told them if they can hep me clean it and make it to a 667. But they were struck and said i am on drugs. They said that their isn't any: Revision or anything like that on Jagex. They said they call our "delta" Alpha. They call 667, a Rs2hdx. Then they said it was harder than i expected because 667 is harder to code and that their used to the "Matrix" they said that a 667 was more complicated in adding cache wise. So it ended up being a 735. They said that Runescape was a 735 loading 735 not like 718 loading 745, so basically i'm going to learn Java Runescape way. So this is basically a 735 loading 742, because the items and gfx and some cache are 735, and they don't have time to add it so hopefully when they get the free time they will do it a 742.
[center][size=18pt]Server Info:[/size][/center]
Their isn't anything really much but the npc's and shops i added in: Project Amazed Version 2, and some objects that is in, Alot of scripts/ java coding was added and removed, because Project Insanity is a whole different codes. So this is basically 3% done.
[center][size=18pt]Starting Point:[/size][/center]
[left][size=22pt]March. 26 2013[/size][/left]
[center] [ul][li]All Rs Music around Project Amazed started.[/li] [li]The Maps are almost complete only 2 locations still not done.[/li] [li]All Weapon Sounds + affects.[/li] [li]All 735 Weapons + Armour added.[/li] [li]99% All 735 Weapons + Armour Specials added.[/li] [li]Firemaking Completed[/li] [li]Whole Cache completed.[/li] [li]Whole cleaning process completed.[/li] [li]Characters are 735..[/li][/ul] [/center]
